title: SKisM - Division Series Part 4 (2012) [Dubstep/Electro House]
description:
-============================-
Label: Never Say Die Records
Artist: SKisM
Featuring Artists: Dirtyloud
Genre: Dubstep/Electro House
Released: 2012-11-26
Catalog: NSDX034
-============================-

The second collaborative effort from the two NSD heavyweights comes in the form of the funk-fuelled monster that is Kick It. Wacky disco sampling and crazy synth edits make this a dubstep tune quite unlike any other, and is possibly the most anticipated part of the Division series. 

On the flip, Brazilian electro superstars Dirtyloud have delivered a remix of outstanding class. Taking a more minimal approach to the modern complextro sound, the duo has managed to keep the vibe of the original while twisting it into a peak time 4x4 stomper.


** PLEASE SEED TO KEEP THE TORRENT ALIVE! **

-=====================-
